Antipodes
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:[Spec. use of antipodes places on the Earth directly opposite each other OED2 3.; AND 1833 Aust.] Australia and New Zealand (often capital), usu. constr. with the, NZ as the British antipodes. (Contrast Down Under.)
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
